Template: onlyoffice/integration-license-acceptance
Type: boolean
Default: false
Description: Do you accept the license agreement terms?
 In order to install ONLYOFFICE Integration Edition, you must accept the ONLYOFFICE Integration Edition LICENSE AGREEMENT terms. If you decline to accept it, the installation will be canceled.

Template: onlyoffice/opensource-license-acceptance
Type: boolean
Default: false
Description: Do you accept the license agreement terms?
 In order to install ONLYOFFICE Integration Edition, you must accept the GNU AFFERO GENERAL PUBLIC LICENSE version 3 terms. If you decline to accept it, the installation will be canceled.

Template: onlyoffice/integration-license-error
Type: error
Description: Declined ONLYOFFICE Integration Edition LICENSE AGREEMENT
 If you do not agree to the ONLYOFFICE Integration Edition LICENSE AGREEMENT terms, you cannot proceed with the installation.

Template: onlyoffice/opensource-license-error
Type: error
Description: Declined GNU AFFERO GENERAL PUBLIC LICENSE
 If you do not agree to the GNU AFFERO GENERAL PUBLIC LICENSE terms, you cannot proceed with the installation.
